title: Is there a picture of Trump's children with Liv Barnas and Igor Froman?
subtitle: There are real pictures of Donald Trump with men arrested on suspicion that they're planning to spend foreign money on his campaign.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A photograph of the adult children of American President Donald Trump-Evanca, Eric and Donald Trump Jr. appears with Lev Barnas and Igor Froman.
